---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LandingNav from '../components/landing/LandingNav.astro';
import LandingFooter from '../components/landing/LandingFooter.astro';
import WaitlistIsland from '../components/WaitlistIsland.tsx';
---
<BaseLayout>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white pt-20">
    <LandingNav />

    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Intelligent Bid Estimation and Schedule Planning{" "}
          <span class="text-blue-600">for the Construction Industry</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Upload your historical documents, connect to your existing apps, and access AI-powered construction solutions &ndash; all in one platform
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
          <WaitlistIsland
            client:idle
            buttonClassName="text-lg px-8 py-3 h-12"
            variant="primary"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">5x</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Faster bids. More hours back for the work only builders can do.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">15%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Higher win rates when teams bid with dynamic data, not a stale price book.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">20%</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Fewer costly errors when context moves seamlessly across Preconstruction and Construction phases.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-100">
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center m-12 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold">Complete Construction Intelligence Platform</div>
      <p class="text-2xl text-center text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">From initial planning to project completion, ConstructWise provides differentiated AI-powered solutions for your numeric bid &amp; schedule data</p>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
            <!-- Table / spreadsheet icon (lucide table) -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-table h-12 w-12 text-blue-600" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v18"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="3" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 9h18"></path><path d="M3 15h18"></path></svg>
            <div class="text-xl font-semibold my-2">Cost Estimates</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">The entire bid preparation process, distilled into one, easy platform that adapts to how your company actually performs. Add context. Get the estimate. Refine with confidence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
            <!-- CalendarCheck2 icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-12 w-12 text-blue-600"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="m9 16 2 2 4-4"></path></svg>
            <div class="text-xl font-semibold my-2">Schedules</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Scheduling used to require a separate tool. ConstructWise generates the CPM schedule from the same context that built the bid &mdash; and acts as your planning teammate to manage and optimize.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-100">
            <!-- User icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-12 w-12 text-blue-600"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg>
            <div class="text-xl font-semibold my-2">Forecasting</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Every bid and schedule, run against thousands of possible futures before you submit. See the risk. Know your chances.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Generate High Quality Cost Estimates</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Transform your proposal process with ConstructWise's advanced AI engine. Generate comprehensive, tailored proposals in a fraction of the time, so you can:
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                <span>Spend more time focusing on the client</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                <span>Check the project details in a way only a human could</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-600 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
                <span>Think on a deeper level about the project strategy, risks, and action plans</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-inner">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 560 315" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
                <!-- App chrome -->
                <rect width="560" height="315" fill="white"/>
                <!-- Header bar -->
                <rect x="20" y="16" width="520" height="36" rx="6" fill="#f8fafc"/>
                <rect x="32" y="26" width="80" height="16" rx="4" fill="#2563eb"/>
                <rect x="130" y="26" width="50" height="16" rx="4" fill="#e2e8f0"/>
                <rect x="196" y="26" width="50" height="16" rx="4" fill="#e2e8f0"/>
                <!-- Spreadsheet: cost estimate rows -->
                <rect x="20" y="64" width="520" height="28" rx="4" fill="#eff6ff"/>
                <text x="32" y="83" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#1e40af">CSI Division</text>
                <text x="180" y="83" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#1e40af">Description</text>
                <text x="340" y="83" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#1e40af">Qty</text>
                <text x="400" y="83" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#1e40af">Unit Cost</text>
                <text x="480" y="83" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#1e40af">Total</text>
                <!-- Row 1 -->
                <rect x="20" y="96" width="520" height="26" rx="0" fill="white"/>
                <line x1="20" y1="122" x2="540" y2="122" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="32" y="113" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">03 30 00</text>
                <text x="180" y="113" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Cast-in-Place Concrete</text>
                <text x="340" y="113" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">2,450 CY</text>
                <text x="400" y="113" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">$185.00</text>
                <text x="480" y="113" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#1e3a5f">$453,250</text>
                <!-- Row 2 -->
                <rect x="20" y="122" width="520" height="26" rx="0" fill="#fafbfd"/>
                <line x1="20" y1="148" x2="540" y2="148" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="32" y="139" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">05 12 00</text>
                <text x="180" y="139" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Structural Steel Framing</text>
                <text x="340" y="139" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">186 TON</text>
                <text x="400" y="139" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">$4,200.00</text>
                <text x="480" y="139" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#1e3a5f">$781,200</text>
                <!-- Row 3 -->
                <rect x="20" y="148" width="520" height="26" rx="0" fill="white"/>
                <line x1="20" y1="174" x2="540" y2="174" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="32" y="165" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">26 00 00</text>
                <text x="180" y="165" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Electrical</text>
                <text x="340" y="165" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">1 LS</text>
                <text x="400" y="165" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">$920,000</text>
                <text x="480" y="165" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#1e3a5f">$920,000</text>
                <!-- Row 4 -->
                <rect x="20" y="174" width="520" height="26" rx="0" fill="#fafbfd"/>
                <line x1="20" y1="200" x2="540" y2="200" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="32" y="191" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">09 90 00</text>
                <text x="180" y="191" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Painting &amp; Coating</text>
                <text x="340" y="191" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">48,000 SF</text>
                <text x="400" y="191" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">$3.75</text>
                <text x="480" y="191" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#1e3a5f">$180,000</text>
                <!-- AI confidence badge -->
                <rect x="20" y="216" width="520" height="44" rx="8" fill="#f0fdf4"/>
                <rect x="32" y="226" width="10" height="10" rx="5" fill="#22c55e"/>
                <text x="50" y="235" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#166534">AI Confidence: 94%</text>
                <text x="200" y="235" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Based on 12 similar past projects</text>
                <!-- Cost summary bar -->
                <rect x="32" y="244" width="200" height="6" rx="3" fill="#bbf7d0"/>
                <rect x="32" y="244" width="188" height="6" rx="3" fill="#22c55e"/>
                <!-- Total -->
                <rect x="20" y="272" width="520" height="30" rx="6" fill="#1e40af"/>
                <text x="32" y="291" font-family="system-ui" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="white">Project Total</text>
                <text x="440" y="291" font-family="system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="white">$2,334,450</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-white rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 560 315" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
                <rect width="560" height="315" fill="white"/>
                <!-- Header -->
                <rect x="20" y="16" width="520" height="36" rx="6" fill="#f8fafc"/>
                <rect x="32" y="26" width="100" height="16" rx="4" fill="#2563eb"/>
                <rect x="148" y="26" width="60" height="16" rx="4" fill="#e2e8f0"/>
                <!-- Gantt chart header -->
                <rect x="20" y="64" width="140" height="24" rx="4" fill="#eff6ff"/>
                <text x="32" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#1e40af">Activity</text>
                <!-- Timeline months -->
                <text x="180" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Jan</text>
                <text x="228" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Feb</text>
                <text x="276" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Mar</text>
                <text x="324" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Apr</text>
                <text x="372" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">May</text>
                <text x="420" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Jun</text>
                <text x="468" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Jul</text>
                <text x="516" y="80" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8">Aug</text>
                <!-- Grid lines -->
                <line x1="170" y1="64" x2="170" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1"/>
                <line x1="218" y1="88" x2="218" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <line x1="266" y1="88" x2="266" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <line x1="314" y1="88" x2="314" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <line x1="362" y1="88" x2="362" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <line x1="410" y1="88" x2="410" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <line x1="458" y1="88" x2="458" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <line x1="506" y1="88" x2="506" y2="270" stroke="#f1f5f9" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
                <!-- Row 1: Site Preparation -->
                <text x="32" y="108" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Site Preparation</text>
                <rect x="180" y="96" width="72" height="18" rx="4" fill="#2563eb"/>
                <!-- Row 2: Foundation -->
                <text x="32" y="136" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Foundation</text>
                <rect x="240" y="124" width="96" height="18" rx="4" fill="#3b82f6"/>
                <!-- Row 3: Structural Steel -->
                <text x="32" y="164" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Structural Steel</text>
                <rect x="314" y="152" width="120" height="18" rx="4" fill="#60a5fa"/>
                <!-- Row 4: MEP Rough-in -->
                <text x="32" y="192" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">MEP Rough-in</text>
                <rect x="362" y="180" width="96" height="18" rx="4" fill="#93c5fd"/>
                <!-- Row 5: Exterior Envelope -->
                <text x="32" y="220" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Exterior Envelope</text>
                <rect x="410" y="208" width="96" height="18" rx="4" fill="#818cf8"/>
                <!-- Row 6: Interior Finishes -->
                <text x="32" y="248" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Interior Finishes</text>
                <rect x="458" y="236" width="72" height="18" rx="4" fill="#a78bfa"/>
                <!-- Dependency arrows -->
                <path d="M252 114 L252 120 L248 124" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
                <path d="M336 142 L336 148 L322 152" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
                <path d="M434 170 L434 176 L370 180" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
                <!-- Critical path indicator -->
                <rect x="20" y="272" width="520" height="30" rx="6" fill="#fef3c7"/>
                <rect x="32" y="282" width="8" height="8" rx="4" fill="#f59e0b"/>
                <text x="48" y="290" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" font-weight="600" fill="#92400e">Critical Path: 214 days</text>
                <text x="240" y="290" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#78716c">Float available on 3 activities</text>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Construction Schedule Optimization</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
              Leverage our intelligence platform to create and optimize construction schedules based on your company's historical data. Model your timelines, resource needs, and potential risks before making decisions.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">95% accuracy</div>
                <span class="text-gray-700">In timeline predictions</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">40% reduction</div>
                <span class="text-gray-700">In project delays</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Seamless Integration &amp; Actionable Insights</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
              Connect to your existing apps and pull your relevant construction data into one place. Get actionable insights through ConstructWise's conversational chat to make better decisions, based on your company's own job histories
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Multiple Integrations</div>
                <span class="text-gray-700">With popular construction apps</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">Actionable insights</div>
                <span class="text-gray-700">From all your historical bid and project data</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-inner">
            <div class="aspect-video bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 560 315" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
                <rect width="560" height="315" fill="white"/>
                <!-- Chat interface header -->
                <rect x="20" y="16" width="520" height="36" rx="6" fill="#f8fafc"/>
                <rect x="32" y="26" width="12" height="12" rx="6" fill="#22c55e"/>
                <text x="50" y="35" font-family="system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600" fill="#1e3a5f">ConstructWise AI</text>
                <!-- Connected apps badges -->
                <rect x="320" y="22" width="56" height="22" rx="11" fill="#eff6ff" stroke="#bfdbfe" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="332" y="37" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" font-weight="500" fill="#2563eb">Procore</text>
                <rect x="384" y="22" width="36" height="22" rx="11" fill="#eff6ff" stroke="#bfdbfe" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="393" y="37" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" font-weight="500" fill="#2563eb">P6</text>
                <rect x="428" y="22" width="50" height="22" rx="11" fill="#eff6ff" stroke="#bfdbfe" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="437" y="37" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" font-weight="500" fill="#2563eb">Egnyte</text>
                <rect x="486" y="22" width="44" height="22" rx="11" fill="#f0fdf4" stroke="#bbf7d0" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="494" y="37" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" font-weight="500" fill="#16a34a">+40</text>
                <!-- User message -->
                <rect x="200" y="68" width="340" height="36" rx="12" fill="#2563eb"/>
                <text x="216" y="90" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="white">How does our concrete cost compare to last 5 bids?</text>
                <!-- AI response -->
                <rect x="20" y="116" width="400" height="120" rx="12" fill="#f8fafc" stroke="#e2e8f0" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="36" y="136" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">Your concrete costs are trending 12% above your</text>
                <text x="36" y="150" font-family="system-ui" font-size="10" fill="#475569">5-bid average. Here's the breakdown:</text>
                <!-- Mini bar chart inside response -->
                <rect x="36" y="162" width="16" height="52" rx="3" fill="#bfdbfe"/>
                <rect x="58" y="172" width="16" height="42" rx="3" fill="#bfdbfe"/>
                <rect x="80" y="168" width="16" height="46" rx="3" fill="#bfdbfe"/>
                <rect x="102" y="178" width="16" height="36" rx="3" fill="#bfdbfe"/>
                <rect x="124" y="158" width="16" height="56" rx="3" fill="#f87171"/>
                <text x="36" y="226" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" fill="#94a3b8">Bid 1</text>
                <text x="58" y="226" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" fill="#94a3b8">Bid 2</text>
                <text x="80" y="226" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" fill="#94a3b8">Bid 3</text>
                <text x="102" y="226" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" fill="#94a3b8">Bid 4</text>
                <text x="120" y="226" font-family="system-ui" font-size="8" font-weight="600" fill="#ef4444">Current</text>
                <!-- Insight callout -->
                <rect x="180" y="162" width="224" height="52" rx="8" fill="#fefce8" stroke="#fde68a" stroke-width="1"/>
                <text x="196" y="182" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" font-weight="600" fill="#92400e">Recommendation</text>
                <text x="196" y="196" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#78716c">Consider rebidding concrete sub</text>
                <text x="196" y="208" font-family="system-ui" font-size="9" fill="#78716c">based on regional pricing data</text>
